<H3><PRE>
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">    Dm
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">C.  Behold, our mirror is the Lord!
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">    Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    Open your eyes and look at yourselves in him
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">    Gm                          A7
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    and you will see how your face is.

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">         Dm
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">A.  Alleluia, alleluia, alleluia.
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">    Gm
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">C.  Alleluia, alleluia, alleluia.
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">    A7                                
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">A.  Glorify his Spirit!
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    Glorify his Spirit!  (Repeat Alleluia)

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">    Dm
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">C.  Wipe away the dirt from your face;
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">    Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    love his holiness and clothe yourselves in it;
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">    Gm                                   A7
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    then you will be immaculate always before him.

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">         Dm
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">A.  Alleluia, alleluia, alleluia.
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">    Gm
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">C.  Alleluia, alleluia, alleluia.
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">    A7                               
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">A.  Give glory to his Spirit!
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    Give glory to his Spirit!
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                        Dm
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    Give glory to his Spirit!
